            <title>[LUCENE-2267] Add solr&apos;s artifact signing scripts into lucene&apos;s build.xml/common-build.xml</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-2267</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;Solr has nice artifact signing scripts in its common-build.xml and build.xml.&lt;/p&gt;

